TopicTitle: Looking for a Python part cfg parser

Articles.Content:
Hi all.

I'm hoping it is a legitimate request and place.

I've started to work on an idea that I had (a kind of an external, sortable part catalog), so I looked at the structure of a sample part cfg file to get an idea about the parser that I will have to implement.

Before I'm going ahead and start working on such a parser, I thought I'd ask if someone already has such a parser lying around and doesn't care to share
